OL,6,FDrone images have revealed the scale
OL,7,Fof the damage caused to a former
OL,8,FSwansea school building.
OL,10,FSeveral fire crews were called to the
OL,11,Fderelict Gorseinon Junior School on
OL,12,FPontardulais Road, Swansea, on 20
OL,13,FSeptember at 3.04pm.
OL,15,FCrews were using hose reel jets and
OL,16,Fbreathing apparatus to fight the fire.
OL,17,FPeople and businesses in the area were
OL,18,Fwarned to follow some regulations
OL,19,Fwhile the incident was ongoing.
