OL,6,FA spokesperson for Swansea Council
OL,7,Fconfirmed on Friday that the fire
OL,8,Fhappened on the grounds of the former
OL,9,Fschool.
OL,11,FThey added that the building is owned
OL,12,Fby the council, but has not been in
OL,13,Fuse for "a number of years."
OL,15,FIn an updated statement on their
OL,16,FFacebook page, Mid and West Wales Fire
OL,17,Fand Rescue Service said: "If you are
OL,18,Fin an area affected by smoke, you are
OL,19,Fadvised to stay indoors, close windows
OL,20,Fand doors, and turn off any air
OL,21,Fconditioning or ventilation units.
