OL,6,F"Motorists who must travel through
OL,7,Fareas affected by smoke should keep
OL,8,Fwindows closed, turn off air
OL,9,Fconditioning and keep air vents
OL,10,Fclosed."
OL,12,FOn Saturday morning, a spokesperson
OL,13,Ffor Mid and West Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,14,FService confirmed that a stop message
OL,15,Fwas received at 8.03pm on Friday
OL,16,Fevening.
OL,18,FThey added that there was no further
OL,19,Finvestigation and the incident was
OL,20,Fclosed.
